  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 400 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "Season the white fish with salt and black pepper.",
    "Place the fish on a baking sheet lined with parchment paper and bake for 12 minutes.",
    "While the fish is baking, toast the bread slices until lightly browned.",
    "In a small bowl, whisk together the fish sauce, lemon juice, and sesame oil.",
    "Once the fish is done, brush the fish sauce mixture evenly over the top of the fish.",
    "Top each slice of toast with a piece of the fish, some grated daikon, and chopped scallions.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy.",
    "Garnish with additional scallions and sesame seeds if desired."
  ],
